[rock music]

00:00:07.649 --> 00:00:15.732
♪ ♪

00:00:21.342 --> 00:00:24.583
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:24.583 --> 00:00:35.070
♪ ♪

00:01:54.830 --> 00:01:56.867
[explosions]

00:02:09.291 --> 00:02:11.563
&gt;&gt; SCREENING SHIELD, CLASS 8!

00:02:11.563 --> 00:02:12.331
&gt;&gt; MIRROR ARMOR PLATING’S

00:02:12.331 --> 00:02:13.901
DETACHING!

00:02:13.901 --> 00:02:16.406
&gt;&gt; BLOCK 3865 HAS BEEN HIT.

00:02:16.406 --> 00:02:17.408
&gt;&gt; Xo: DAMAGE?

00:02:17.408 --> 00:02:18.410
&gt;&gt; MINIMAL, BUT OUR THRUSTER

00:02:18.410 --> 00:02:19.312
FLAME’S VISIBLE NOW.

00:02:19.312 --> 00:02:20.581
&gt;&gt; Captain: STAND FAST, MEN.

00:02:20.581 --> 00:02:21.550
LET’S TEACH THEM A LITTLE

00:02:21.550 --> 00:02:22.786
SOMETHING.

00:02:22.786 --> 00:02:24.155
TEACH THEM EXACTLY WHO THEY’RE

00:02:24.155 --> 00:02:25.457
FACING.

00:02:25.457 --> 00:02:26.827
&gt;&gt; ENEMY FLEET SIZE IS OFF THE

00:02:26.827 --> 00:02:27.562
CHARTS!

00:02:27.562 --> 00:02:29.465
&gt;&gt; Xo: SO ALL THE LIGHTS IN THE

00:02:29.465 --> 00:02:31.904
HEAVENS ARE OUR ENEMY NOW, EH?

00:02:31.904 --> 00:02:33.607
&gt;&gt; Captain: YEAH, BUT THEY’RE

00:02:33.607 --> 00:02:35.177
WORTHY OPPONENTS.

00:02:35.177 --> 00:02:35.878
I’LL USE THE FABRIC OF

00:02:35.878 --> 00:02:37.381
SPACE‐TIME TO WRING THEM OUT OF

00:02:37.381 --> 00:02:40.521
EXISTENCE.

00:02:40.521 --> 00:02:41.389
&gt;&gt; Xo: ALL RIGHT, PREPARE TO

00:02:41.389 --> 00:02:42.859
FIRE MAELSTROM CANNON.

00:02:42.859 --> 00:02:44.228
TARGET THE GREAT DIMENSIONAL

00:02:44.228 --> 00:02:46.867
WATERFALL.

00:02:46.867 --> 00:02:48.336
&gt;&gt; Captain: GURREN LAGANN!

00:02:48.336 --> 00:02:49.372
SPIN ON!

00:02:49.372 --> 00:02:52.311
WHO THE HELL DO YOU THINK I AM?

00:02:52.311 --> 00:02:53.313
[adventurous music]

00:02:53.313 --> 00:03:01.396
♪ ♪

00:03:12.217 --> 00:03:13.921
&gt;&gt; Simon: DIGGING TUNNELS,

00:03:13.921 --> 00:03:16.860
DAY AFTER DAY, THAT’S MY JOB.

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:19.198
THE MORE WE DIG, THE MORE THE

00:03:19.198 --> 00:03:21.369
VILLAGE CAN EXPAND.

00:03:21.369 --> 00:03:23.708
WHEN THE VILLAGE CHIEF IS HAPPY,

00:03:23.708 --> 00:03:26.479
HE FEEDS ME PIG‐MOLE STEAKS.

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:28.918
DO I JUST DIG FOR THE STEAKS?

00:03:28.918 --> 00:03:32.726
NO, NOT EXACTLY.

00:03:32.726 --> 00:03:40.808
[inquisitive gasps]

00:03:43.547 --> 00:03:45.250
I ALSO DO IT SO I CAN DIG UP

00:03:45.250 --> 00:03:47.922
TREASURE.

00:03:47.922 --> 00:03:48.891
&gt;&gt; Mayor: COME ON, NOW.

00:03:48.891 --> 00:03:56.439
KEEP DIGGING!

00:03:56.439 --> 00:03:59.311
HEY, WHY CAN’T ANY OF YOU LOSERS

00:03:59.311 --> 00:04:00.480
DIG LIKE THAT GUY?

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:03.219
DON’T YOU WANT THOSE STEAKS?

00:04:03.219 --> 00:04:06.794
[giggles]

00:04:06.794 --> 00:04:08.664
&gt;&gt; EWW, LOOK. IT’S SIMON THE

00:04:08.664 --> 00:04:09.331
DIGGER.

00:04:09.331 --> 00:04:10.400
&gt;&gt; I DON’T GET IT.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:12.404
WHAT’S THE FUN OF GETTING ALL

00:04:12.404 --> 00:04:13.339
COVERED IN DIRT DAY AFTER DAY?

00:04:13.339 --> 00:04:14.241
&gt;&gt; AND HE’S CARRYING

00:04:14.241 --> 00:04:15.377
SOMETHING WEIRD TOO.

00:04:15.377 --> 00:04:15.945
&gt;&gt; HE’S SO GROSS.

00:04:15.945 --> 00:04:17.515
&gt;&gt; AND HE SMELLS.

00:04:17.515 --> 00:04:18.717
&gt;&gt; HE’S LOOKING AT US.

00:04:18.717 --> 00:04:20.020
&gt;&gt; IF WE’RE NOT CAREFUL, HE

00:04:20.020 --> 00:04:21.289
MIGHT DRILL A HOLE IN US TOO!

00:04:21.289 --> 00:04:27.334
[laughter]

00:04:33.313 --> 00:04:34.516
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WALK WITH YOUR HEAD

00:04:34.516 --> 00:04:35.885
HELD HIGH, SIMON.

00:04:35.885 --> 00:04:38.791
&gt;&gt; Simon: KAMINA?

00:04:38.791 --> 00:04:40.728
&gt;&gt; Kamina: DON’T CALL ME KAMINA,

00:04:40.728 --> 00:04:42.699
CALL ME "BRO."

00:04:42.699 --> 00:04:44.603
&gt;&gt; Simon: UM, I DON’T HAVE ANY

00:04:44.603 --> 00:04:45.370
SIBLINGS.

00:04:45.370 --> 00:04:46.372
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, IT’S NOT ABOUT

00:04:46.372 --> 00:04:46.974
BLOOD.

00:04:46.974 --> 00:04:48.343
YOU AND ME ARE SOUL BROTHERS.

00:04:48.343 --> 00:04:49.746
YOU KNOW, WE’RE SIBLINGS OF THE

00:04:49.746 --> 00:04:50.848
SPIRIT!

00:04:50.848 --> 00:04:52.017
DON’T WORRY ABOUT WHAT THOSE

00:04:52.017 --> 00:04:53.888
STUPID UGLY CHICKS SAY.

00:04:53.888 --> 00:04:55.825
THIS LOOKS PRETTY GOOD ON YOU,

00:04:55.825 --> 00:04:57.494
KID.

00:04:57.494 --> 00:04:58.363
DRILLS ARE YOUR SOUL.

00:04:58.363 --> 00:04:59.666
YOU GOT IT?

00:04:59.666 --> 00:05:03.774
NOW, COME ON.

00:05:03.774 --> 00:05:05.912
GENTLEMEN, SORRY FOR THE DELAY!

00:05:05.912 --> 00:05:07.047
ARE YOU GUYS READY?

00:05:07.047 --> 00:05:08.049
&gt;&gt; JUST ABOUT.

00:05:08.049 --> 00:05:09.285
&gt;&gt; Simon: UM, WHAT IS IT YOU’RE

00:05:09.285 --> 00:05:09.786
DOING?

00:05:09.786 --> 00:05:11.289
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LISTEN UP, SIMON.

00:05:11.289 --> 00:05:12.525
THAT DRILL THERE DOES NOT BELONG

00:05:12.525 --> 00:05:13.794
TO THE VILLAGE CHIEF, ’CAUSE

00:05:13.794 --> 00:05:15.765
THAT DRILL IS WHO YOU ARE!

00:05:15.765 --> 00:05:16.934
SIMON, YOURS IS THE DRILL THAT

00:05:16.934 --> 00:05:18.436
WILL BREAK THROUGH THE VAULT OF

00:05:18.436 --> 00:05:19.405
HEAVEN!

00:05:19.405 --> 00:05:20.508
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT WHY?

00:05:20.508 --> 00:05:21.777
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I HAVE IT ALL FIGURED

00:05:21.777 --> 00:05:22.377
OUT!

00:05:22.377 --> 00:05:23.681
DON’T ASK QUESTIONS!

00:05:23.681 --> 00:05:25.317
&gt;&gt; Simon: MEANING THAT YOU CAN’T

00:05:25.317 --> 00:05:25.785
EXPLAIN ANYTHING.

00:05:25.785 --> 00:05:26.787
&gt;&gt; Kamina: ALL RIGHT, YOU BOZOS,

00:05:26.787 --> 00:05:28.323
WE READY TO GO?

00:05:28.323 --> 00:05:29.058
&gt;&gt; YEAH!

00:05:29.058 --> 00:05:30.060
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WE’RE THE INVINCIBLE

00:05:30.060 --> 00:05:31.530
TEAM GURREN.

00:05:31.530 --> 00:05:32.999
NOBODY CAN STAND IN OUR WAY.

00:05:32.999 --> 00:05:34.636
&gt;&gt; UH, YEAH.

00:05:34.636 --> 00:05:35.805
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WE’RE SICK OF BEING

00:05:35.805 --> 00:05:36.773
COOPED UP IN THIS LITTLE TOWN!

00:05:36.773 --> 00:05:37.842
IT’S THE YOUNG WHO ARE GONNA

00:05:37.842 --> 00:05:38.944
BREAK OUT.

00:05:38.944 --> 00:05:40.915
YOUTH OF THIS TOWN, AIM FOR THE

00:05:40.915 --> 00:05:44.623
SURFACE!

00:05:44.623 --> 00:05:47.394
[screams]

00:05:47.394 --> 00:05:49.833
&gt;&gt; YAHOO!

00:05:49.833 --> 00:05:51.637
STEP ASIDE, MAKE WAY!

00:05:51.637 --> 00:05:53.072
TEAM GURREN IS COMING THROUGH!

00:05:53.072 --> 00:05:55.110
[screaming]

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:57.347
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT NOW?

00:05:57.347 --> 00:05:58.082
&gt;&gt; Kamina: ALL RIGHT, LISTEN UP,

00:05:58.082 --> 00:05:58.684
SIMON.

00:05:58.684 --> 00:05:59.920
WE’RE GONNA USE YOUR DRILL TO

00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:00.988
BUST THROUGH THAT CEILING UP

00:06:00.988 --> 00:06:01.723
THERE.

00:06:01.723 --> 00:06:02.992
BUST THROUGH THAT, AND THE NEXT

00:06:02.992 --> 00:06:03.861
STOP IS ALL THE WAY TO THE

00:06:03.861 --> 00:06:04.863
SURFACE.

00:06:04.863 --> 00:06:06.032
WE’RE GONNA MAKE A BREAK FOR IT

00:06:06.032 --> 00:06:07.702
AND GET OUT OF THIS PLACE!

00:06:07.702 --> 00:06:08.971
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS IS INSANE!

00:06:08.971 --> 00:06:10.942
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU CAN DO IT!

00:06:10.942 --> 00:06:12.110
[squeaks]

00:06:12.110 --> 00:06:15.551
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHEN DID YOU‐‐

00:06:15.551 --> 00:06:16.720
&gt;&gt; Kamina: CHARGE!

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.924
KEEP GOING STRAIGHT AHEAD.

00:06:18.924 --> 00:06:23.366
[screaming]

00:06:23.366 --> 00:06:26.673
FLY, PIGGIES!

00:06:26.673 --> 00:06:27.642
&gt;&gt; Mayor: KAMINA!

00:06:27.642 --> 00:06:28.844
I SHOULD’VE KNOWN IT’D BE YOU

00:06:28.844 --> 00:06:29.478
AGAIN.

00:06:29.478 --> 00:06:30.480
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU’D BETTER STEP

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:31.516
ASIDE.

00:06:31.516 --> 00:06:37.662
&gt;&gt; Mayor: YOU LITTLE MORON!

00:06:40.968 --> 00:06:42.371
&gt;&gt; Mayor: WOULD YOU PEOPLE COME

00:06:42.371 --> 00:06:43.139
TO YOUR SENSES?

00:06:43.139 --> 00:06:45.043
THIS MYSTERIOUS "SURFACE" OF

00:06:45.043 --> 00:06:46.145
YOURS DOESN’T EXIST!

00:06:46.145 --> 00:06:47.715
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LIKE HELL IT DOESN’T!

00:06:47.715 --> 00:06:49.018
I’VE SEEN IT MYSELF.

00:06:49.018 --> 00:06:50.086
UP ON THE SURFACE, THERE’S NO

00:06:50.086 --> 00:06:50.788
WALLS!

00:06:50.788 --> 00:06:51.556
NO CEILING!

00:06:51.556 --> 00:06:52.926
INSTEAD, ALL YOU SEE AROUND YOU

00:06:52.926 --> 00:06:54.061
IS A BRIGHT BLUE SKY.

00:06:54.061 --> 00:06:55.463
&gt;&gt; Mayor: A LIAR’S SON IS A LIAR

00:06:55.463 --> 00:06:56.399
TOO.

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:57.167
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT’S THAT?

00:06:57.167 --> 00:06:57.902
&gt;&gt; Mayor: YOUR OLD MAN DID

00:06:57.902 --> 00:06:58.871
NOTHING BUT SPOUT CRAP LIKE

00:06:58.871 --> 00:07:00.106
THAT.

00:07:00.106 --> 00:07:01.843
AND WHAT DID IT GET HIM?

00:07:01.843 --> 00:07:03.012
DEAD AND BURIED UNDER A BIG

00:07:03.012 --> 00:07:04.081
PILE OF ROCKS SOMEWHERE!

00:07:04.081 --> 00:07:04.916
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU’RE WRONG!

00:07:04.916 --> 00:07:06.118
MY DAD MADE IT TO THE SURFACE!

00:07:06.118 --> 00:07:07.120
I KNOW ’CAUSE I WAS THERE WITH

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:07.655
HIM!

00:07:07.655 --> 00:07:08.724
&gt;&gt; Mayor: THEN WHAT ARE YOU

00:07:08.724 --> 00:07:10.026
DOING HERE, SMART GUY?

00:07:10.026 --> 00:07:11.128
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WELL, I‐‐

00:07:11.128 --> 00:07:12.865
&gt;&gt; Mayor: OKAY, NOW GET THIS!

00:07:12.865 --> 00:07:15.470
THIS VILLAGE IS ALL WE HAVE!

00:07:15.470 --> 00:07:16.405
FOR UNTOLD GENERATIONS, WE’VE

00:07:16.405 --> 00:07:18.142
BEEN WARNED TO NEVER UNSEAL THE

00:07:18.142 --> 00:07:20.180
CANOPY THAT KEEPS US SAFE.

00:07:20.180 --> 00:07:21.449
PEOPLE WHO DON’T UNDERSTAND THAT

00:07:21.449 --> 00:07:23.019
RULE DON’T GET TO EAT.

00:07:23.019 --> 00:07:24.421
TO THE STOCKADE WITH YOU!

00:07:24.421 --> 00:07:26.727
WITHOUT FOOD!

00:07:26.727 --> 00:07:28.429
&gt;&gt; WE’RE SO SORRY, SIR!

00:07:28.429 --> 00:07:29.031
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU WEASELS!

00:07:29.031 --> 00:07:31.703
[Mayor laughs]

00:07:31.703 --> 00:07:33.473
&gt;&gt; SORRY, BRO!

00:07:33.473 --> 00:07:34.542
HAD TO DO IT.

00:07:34.542 --> 00:07:35.778
&gt;&gt; NO DINNER IS A HIGH PRICE TO

00:07:35.778 --> 00:07:36.145
PAY.

00:07:36.145 --> 00:07:37.649
&gt;&gt; COME ON, BRO, SWALLOW YOUR

00:07:37.649 --> 00:07:39.051
PRIDE AND APOLOGIZE TOO.

00:07:39.051 --> 00:07:40.655
&gt;&gt; Kamina: DON’T CALL ME "BRO."

00:07:40.655 --> 00:07:42.457
I DON’T EVER WANNA BE CALLED

00:07:42.457 --> 00:07:43.861
"BRO" BY THE LIKES OF YOU THREE

00:07:43.861 --> 00:07:46.499
BACK‐STABBING LOSERS!

00:07:46.499 --> 00:07:48.469
HMPH!

00:07:48.469 --> 00:07:49.606
&gt;&gt; Mayor: THE BONDS OF LOYALTY

00:07:49.606 --> 00:07:50.508
DON’T RUN DEEP IN THIS TEAM

00:07:50.508 --> 00:07:51.442
GURREN OF YOURS.

00:07:51.442 --> 00:07:53.446
SIMON, YOU COME TOO.

00:07:53.446 --> 00:07:54.214
[gasps]

00:07:54.214 --> 00:07:56.018
&gt;&gt; I KNOW THAT KAMINA ROPED YOU

00:07:56.018 --> 00:07:57.822
INTO HELPING HIM.

00:07:57.822 --> 00:07:59.158
YOU HAVE AN IMPORTANT JOB HERE

00:07:59.158 --> 00:08:01.530
IN GIHA VILLAGE: DIGGING TUNNELS

00:08:01.530 --> 00:08:03.099
TO EXPAND THE COMMUNITY.

00:08:03.099 --> 00:08:04.168
YOU DON’T HAVE TO STAY WITH THAT

00:08:04.168 --> 00:08:05.103
IDIOT.

00:08:05.103 --> 00:08:06.573
COME ALONG.

00:08:06.573 --> 00:08:07.542
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT I‐‐

00:08:07.542 --> 00:08:10.113
&gt;&gt; Kamina: GO AHEAD.

00:08:10.113 --> 00:08:11.917
DON’T SWEAT IT.

00:08:11.917 --> 00:08:12.785
GO ON.

00:08:12.785 --> 00:08:15.958
[gasps]

00:08:15.958 --> 00:08:19.231
[rumbling]

00:08:19.231 --> 00:08:21.503
&gt;&gt; Mayor: IT’S AN EARTHQUAKE!

00:08:21.503 --> 00:08:22.605
EVERYBODY TAKE COVER!

00:08:22.605 --> 00:08:26.513
[screaming]

00:08:26.513 --> 00:08:27.648
&gt;&gt; Simon: WE GOTTA GET OUT

00:08:27.648 --> 00:08:28.483
OF HERE!

00:08:28.483 --> 00:08:29.786
KAMINA!

00:08:29.786 --> 00:08:30.955
&gt;&gt; Kamina: NO WAY.

00:08:30.955 --> 00:08:31.823
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT‐‐

00:08:31.823 --> 00:08:38.504
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I DON’T RUN AWAY!

00:08:38.504 --> 00:08:39.204
&gt;&gt; Simon: IF WE DON’T RUN, WE’RE

00:08:39.204 --> 00:08:42.277
GONNA GET CRUSHED HERE AND DIE!

00:08:42.277 --> 00:08:43.781
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THAT’S RIGHT.

00:08:43.781 --> 00:08:44.883
I FORGOT.

00:08:44.883 --> 00:08:47.020
I’M SORRY.

00:08:47.020 --> 00:08:47.922
DON’T WORRY, KID.

00:08:47.922 --> 00:08:53.600
IT’S ALMOST OVER.

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:54.636
ARE YOU PEOPLE GONNA KEEP LIVING

00:08:54.636 --> 00:08:56.540
IN FEAR OF EARTHQUAKES DAY AFTER

00:08:56.540 --> 00:08:57.842
DAY FOR YOUR WHOLE LIVES?

00:08:57.842 --> 00:08:58.944
UP ON THE SURFACE, THERE AIN’T

00:08:58.944 --> 00:09:01.650
NO CEILING!

00:09:01.650 --> 00:09:02.652
&gt;&gt; Mayor: GIVE IT A REST, WILL

00:09:02.652 --> 00:09:03.252
YOU?

00:09:03.252 --> 00:09:04.522
I DIDN’T LOOK AFTER ALL YOU

00:09:04.522 --> 00:09:05.558
ORPHANED KIDS OUT OF THE

00:09:05.558 --> 00:09:06.860
GOODNESS OF MY HEART, YOU KNOW!

00:09:06.860 --> 00:09:08.731
I DID IT BECAUSE I’M THE CHIEF!

00:09:08.731 --> 00:09:09.933
I HAVE A DUTY TO LOOK OUT FOR

00:09:09.933 --> 00:09:12.003
THE WELFARE OF THIS VILLAGE!

00:09:12.003 --> 00:09:13.774
BUT IF YOU PEOPLE CAN’T DO AS I

00:09:13.774 --> 00:09:15.243
TELL YOU, THERE’S NO PLACE FOR

00:09:15.243 --> 00:09:19.552
YOU HERE!

00:09:19.552 --> 00:09:22.257
[humming a tune]

00:09:22.257 --> 00:09:24.061
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, WHAT ARE YOU

00:09:24.061 --> 00:09:25.564
DOING IN HERE?

00:09:25.564 --> 00:09:26.232
[bouncy sound]

00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:27.635
[laughs]

00:09:27.635 --> 00:09:28.704
THAT’S A GOOD BOY.

00:09:28.704 --> 00:09:29.672
[bouncy sound]

00:09:29.672 --> 00:09:30.841
NOW I’VE GOT SOME EMERGENCY

00:09:30.841 --> 00:09:31.843
RATIONS.

00:09:31.843 --> 00:09:33.547
[squeals]

00:09:33.547 --> 00:09:34.549
&gt;&gt; Simon: MY PARENTS DIED IN AN

00:09:34.549 --> 00:09:35.584
EARTHQUAKE.

00:09:35.584 --> 00:09:37.254
IT HAPPENED WHEN I WAS SEVEN.

00:09:37.254 --> 00:09:39.793
NO MATTER HOW MANY HOLES I DIG,

00:09:39.793 --> 00:09:42.297
THE CEILING IS EVENTUALLY GONNA

00:09:42.297 --> 00:09:44.736
FALL AND CRUSH ME, THE CHIEF,

00:09:44.736 --> 00:09:46.272
AND EVERYBODY IN THE VILLAGE,

00:09:46.272 --> 00:09:47.040
AND WE’RE ALL GONNA DIE.

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:48.577
THAT’S A GIVEN.

00:09:48.577 --> 00:09:50.915
THAT’S A FACT OF LIFE.

00:09:50.915 --> 00:09:54.054
OR IS IT?

00:09:54.054 --> 00:09:58.162
[pulsing]

00:09:58.162 --> 00:10:05.176
[gasps]

00:10:05.176 --> 00:10:06.345
&gt;&gt; Mayor: LIGHTS OUT, EVERYBODY!

00:10:06.345 --> 00:10:08.015
TIME FOR LIGHTS OUT!

00:10:08.015 --> 00:10:09.652
PUT OUT THE LIGHTS, IT’S NIGHT

00:10:09.652 --> 00:10:11.222
TIME HOURS!

00:10:11.222 --> 00:10:12.758
BE GOOD CITIZENS AND GO TO

00:10:12.758 --> 00:10:13.894
SLEEP, EVERYONE.

00:10:13.894 --> 00:10:14.929
DON’T WASTE PRECIOUS

00:10:14.929 --> 00:10:17.267
ELECTRICITY!

00:10:17.267 --> 00:10:18.302
&gt;&gt; Kamina: GROW UP BIG AND

00:10:18.302 --> 00:10:20.206
PLUMP, NOW, GROW UP BIG AND

00:10:20.206 --> 00:10:21.041
PLUMP.

00:10:21.041 --> 00:10:22.945
GROW INTO A BIG, FAT, JUICY

00:10:22.945 --> 00:10:23.379
STEAK FOR ME TO EAT.

00:10:23.379 --> 00:10:27.354
[squeals]

00:10:27.354 --> 00:10:28.991
WHAT THE HELL?

00:10:28.991 --> 00:10:30.193
&gt;&gt; Simon: KAMINA!

00:10:30.193 --> 00:10:31.162
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SIMON?

00:10:31.162 --> 00:10:32.030
WHAT’S UP?

00:10:32.030 --> 00:10:33.232
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME ON, THERE’S

00:10:33.232 --> 00:10:34.334
SOMETHING YOU’VE GOT TO SEE!

00:10:34.334 --> 00:10:34.869
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT?

00:10:34.869 --> 00:10:35.704
&gt;&gt; Simon: HURRY UP!

00:10:35.704 --> 00:10:37.340
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YEAH, BUT THAT WOULD

00:10:37.340 --> 00:10:38.710
BE A JAILBREAK.

00:10:38.710 --> 00:10:39.746
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:10:39.746 --> 00:10:41.015
&gt;&gt; IF THE CHIEF FINDS OUT,

00:10:41.015 --> 00:10:42.350
THERE’LL BE HELL TO PAY, SIMON.

00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:44.154
&gt;&gt; Simon: I WAS SO PREOCCUPIED,

00:10:44.154 --> 00:10:45.925
THAT DIDN’T EVEN OCCUR TO ME.

00:10:45.925 --> 00:10:47.127
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WELL, IF WE GET BACK

00:10:47.127 --> 00:10:48.062
BY MORNING, HE’LL BE NONE THE

00:10:48.062 --> 00:10:49.364
WISER.

00:10:49.364 --> 00:10:51.268
SO WHAT IS SO AWFULLY IMPORTANT

00:10:51.268 --> 00:10:52.638
DOWN HERE THAT I HAD TO BUST OUT

00:10:52.638 --> 00:10:54.107
OF JAIL JUST TO SEE IT?

00:10:54.107 --> 00:10:55.143
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT’S A FACE.

00:10:55.143 --> 00:10:56.212
IT’S THIS AWESOME, HUMUNGOUS

00:10:56.212 --> 00:10:59.853
FACE!

00:10:59.853 --> 00:11:01.690
&gt;&gt; Mayor: YOU’VE GOT SOME NERVE

00:11:01.690 --> 00:11:03.727
BREAKING OUT OF JAIL, KAMINA.

00:11:03.727 --> 00:11:05.263
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SIMON, IS THIS THE

00:11:05.263 --> 00:11:06.800
HUMUNGOUS FACE?

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:07.702
&gt;&gt; Mayor: DON’T YOU

00:11:07.702 --> 00:11:08.937
UNDERESTIMATE ME, SONNY!

00:11:08.937 --> 00:11:10.708
I’M THE VILLAGE CHIEF, SO THAT

00:11:10.708 --> 00:11:12.210
MEANS I ALSO STAND GUARD!

00:11:12.210 --> 00:11:14.649
SIMON, THAT GOES FOR YOU TOO.

00:11:14.649 --> 00:11:15.751
I KNOW ALL ABOUT THOSE EXTRA

00:11:15.751 --> 00:11:16.720
TUNNELS YOU’VE BEEN DIGGING IN

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:17.722
SECRET.

00:11:17.722 --> 00:11:19.024
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LEAVE HIM.

00:11:19.024 --> 00:11:20.260
HE HASN’T DONE ANYTHING.

00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:21.730
I’M THE GUILTY ONE.

00:11:21.730 --> 00:11:23.099
&gt;&gt; Mayor: OH, YES, I’M PERFECTLY

00:11:23.099 --> 00:11:28.844
AWARE OF HOW GUILTY YOU ARE!

00:11:28.844 --> 00:11:33.720
[growling]

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.724
[rumbling and screams]

00:11:35.724 --> 00:11:39.464
[gasps]

00:11:39.464 --> 00:11:42.003
[crashing]

00:11:45.410 --> 00:11:48.049
[explosions]

00:11:51.088 --> 00:11:51.990
[ambient electronic music]

00:11:51.990 --> 00:11:58.770
♪ ♪

00:11:58.770 --> 00:12:00.908
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SO SIMON, THIS THING

00:12:00.908 --> 00:12:02.110
YOU WANTED TO SHOW ME...

00:12:02.110 --> 00:12:04.248
IS THIS IT?

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:20.146
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LOOK UP!

00:12:20.146 --> 00:12:21.315
THAT’S THE SURFACE!

00:12:21.315 --> 00:12:22.852
I TOLD YOU THERE WAS A SURFACE

00:12:22.852 --> 00:12:23.954
UP THERE!

00:12:23.954 --> 00:12:25.056
THIS BIG MUG FELL FROM THE

00:12:25.056 --> 00:12:27.494
SURFACE, FROM ABOVE THE CEILING.

00:12:27.494 --> 00:12:28.964
AIN’T THAT RIGHT, MR. CHIEF?

00:12:28.964 --> 00:12:36.980
[crashes and rumbling]

00:12:36.980 --> 00:12:38.817
&gt;&gt; IT’S A MONSTER!

00:12:38.817 --> 00:12:45.096
[screaming]

00:12:45.096 --> 00:12:46.231
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT ARE YOU WAITING

00:12:46.231 --> 00:12:46.967
FOR, CHIEF?

00:12:46.967 --> 00:12:48.069
I THOUGHT YOU SAID THAT IT WAS

00:12:48.069 --> 00:12:49.004
YOUR DUTY TO PROTECT THE

00:12:49.004 --> 00:12:49.505
VILLAGE.

00:12:49.505 --> 00:12:51.442
GOSH, IT’S HARD TO TELL WHICH OF

00:12:51.442 --> 00:12:56.786
US IS THE LIAR NOW, AIN’T IT?

00:12:56.786 --> 00:12:57.888
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO, THIS WAY!

00:12:57.888 --> 00:12:59.224
LET’S GET OUTTA HERE!

00:12:59.224 --> 00:12:59.892
HEY, BRO?

00:12:59.892 --> 00:13:02.531
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

00:13:02.531 --> 00:13:04.134
YOU’VE GOT GUTS, PLOWING INTO MY

00:13:04.134 --> 00:13:05.069
VILLAGE LIKE THIS.

00:13:05.069 --> 00:13:06.773
YOU AND THAT BIG UGLY MUG OF

00:13:06.773 --> 00:13:08.543
YOURS, YOU KNOW THAT?

00:13:08.543 --> 00:13:10.914
&gt;&gt; Simon: RUN!

00:13:10.914 --> 00:13:12.150
&gt;&gt; Kamina: BUT THAT ENDS HERE!

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:13.820
I WON’T STAND FOR ANY MORE OF

00:13:13.820 --> 00:13:15.123
YOUR SHENANIGANS!

00:13:15.123 --> 00:13:19.297
&gt;&gt; WHA‐‐WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

00:13:19.297 --> 00:13:20.433
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, IT TALKED.

00:13:20.433 --> 00:13:22.538
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I’M GONNA TELL YOU

00:13:22.538 --> 00:13:23.774
SOMETHING IMPORTANT, SO YOU

00:13:23.774 --> 00:13:24.542
BETTER DIG THE WAX OUT OF THOSE

00:13:24.542 --> 00:13:25.911
HUGE EARS OF YOURS AND LISTEN

00:13:25.911 --> 00:13:26.412
CLOSE.

00:13:26.412 --> 00:13:27.782
THE REPUTATION OF TEAM GURREN

00:13:27.782 --> 00:13:28.950
ECHOES FAR AND WIDE.

00:13:28.950 --> 00:13:30.119
WHEN THEY TALK ABOUT ITS BADASS

00:13:30.119 --> 00:13:31.088
LEADER, THE MAN OF

00:13:31.088 --> 00:13:32.257
INDOMITABLE SPIRIT AND

00:13:32.257 --> 00:13:35.798
MASCULINITY, THEY’RE TALKING

00:13:35.798 --> 00:13:38.570
ABOUT ME, THE MIGHTY KAMINA!

00:13:38.570 --> 00:13:40.808
&gt;&gt; WHAT AN IDIOT.

00:13:40.808 --> 00:13:41.876
&gt;&gt; WHAT A DUNCE.

00:13:41.876 --> 00:13:44.047
&gt;&gt; WHAT A TOTAL DUMB‐ASS.

00:13:44.047 --> 00:13:45.450
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I, KAMINA, WILL NOT

00:13:45.450 --> 00:13:48.155
TOLERATE ANY FURTHER LAWLESSNESS

00:13:48.155 --> 00:13:49.257
IN THIS VILLAGE!

00:13:49.257 --> 00:13:51.896
[laughs]

00:13:51.896 --> 00:13:53.432
WHAT CAN A PUNY HUMAN LIKE

00:13:53.432 --> 00:13:54.936
YOU DO TO STOP ME?

00:13:54.936 --> 00:14:03.019
[laser blasts]

00:14:08.563 --> 00:14:10.534
&gt;&gt; Yoko: ALL RIGHT, YOU TWO,

00:14:10.534 --> 00:14:11.268
YOU BETTER GET BACK.

00:14:11.268 --> 00:14:12.437
[Kamina whistles]

00:14:12.437 --> 00:14:13.940
SOMETHING ELSE FROM ABOVE?

00:14:13.940 --> 00:14:14.842
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH, AND IT’S A GIRL

00:14:14.842 --> 00:14:15.476
THIS TIME.

00:14:15.476 --> 00:14:18.049
[laser blasts continue]

00:14:18.049 --> 00:14:24.996
[groaning]

00:14:24.996 --> 00:14:25.964
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I ONLY KNOCKED IT

00:14:25.964 --> 00:14:26.566
BACKWARDS.

00:14:26.566 --> 00:14:27.835
IT CAN STILL GET UP AND GET US.

00:14:27.835 --> 00:14:28.469
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, BABE, COME HERE

00:14:28.469 --> 00:14:29.337
OFTEN?

00:14:29.337 --> 00:14:30.039
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT?

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:30.941
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SO YOU’RE GOING TO

00:14:30.941 --> 00:14:31.843
SLUG IT OUT, HUH?

00:14:31.843 --> 00:14:32.945
LET ME HELP OUT.

00:14:32.945 --> 00:14:33.412
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HELP OUT?

00:14:33.412 --> 00:14:34.949
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU CAME FROM THE

00:14:34.949 --> 00:14:35.450
SURFACE, DIDN’T YOU?

00:14:35.450 --> 00:14:36.251
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YEAH, SO WHAT?

00:14:36.251 --> 00:14:37.521
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THAT’S AWESOME.

00:14:37.521 --> 00:14:38.557
SO THAT’S A WEAPON THEY USE ON

00:14:38.557 --> 00:14:39.324
THE SURFACE, HUH?

00:14:39.324 --> 00:14:40.126
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NOT EXACTLY, BUT

00:14:40.126 --> 00:14:41.361
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

00:14:41.361 --> 00:14:42.464
&gt;&gt; Kamina: DAMN, YOU GOT A

00:14:42.464 --> 00:14:43.567
MIGHTY FINE BODY!

00:14:43.567 --> 00:14:45.403
SURFACE CHICKS ARE A BREED

00:14:45.403 --> 00:14:46.371
APART!

00:14:46.371 --> 00:14:47.641
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DO I NEED TO TELL YOU

00:14:47.641 --> 00:14:48.877
AGAIN TO RUN?

00:14:48.877 --> 00:14:50.614
DO YOU HAVE A DEATH WISH?

00:14:50.614 --> 00:14:56.091
[gasping]

00:14:56.091 --> 00:14:58.930
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THANKS A LOT, SIMON!

00:14:58.930 --> 00:14:59.999
REAL NICE SAVE.

00:14:59.999 --> 00:15:00.601
&gt;&gt; Simon: HURRY UP!

00:15:00.601 --> 00:15:01.536
THIS WAY!

00:15:01.536 --> 00:15:02.303
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHERE AM I?

00:15:02.303 --> 00:15:03.472
&gt;&gt; Kamina: GIHA VILLAGE.

00:15:03.472 --> 00:15:04.876
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH, THE PIT NEXT DOOR.

00:15:04.876 --> 00:15:05.644
&gt;&gt; Kamina: NEXT DOOR?

00:15:05.644 --> 00:15:06.946
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M FROM LITTNER

00:15:06.946 --> 00:15:07.982
VILLAGE, THE PIT THAT’S RIGHT

00:15:07.982 --> 00:15:08.917
NEXT TO THIS ONE.

00:15:08.917 --> 00:15:10.019
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT THE HELL?

00:15:10.019 --> 00:15:10.654
YOU SAID YOU’RE FROM THE

00:15:10.654 --> 00:15:11.656
SURFACE, BUT YOU WERE RAISED IN

00:15:11.656 --> 00:15:12.490
A PIT?

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:13.593
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I CAME FROM THE SURFACE

00:15:13.593 --> 00:15:14.562
JUST NOW, BUT I’M ORIGINALLY

00:15:14.562 --> 00:15:15.564
FROM LITTNER.

00:15:15.564 --> 00:15:16.465
&gt;&gt; Kamina: AW, GEEZ, YOU’RE A

00:15:16.465 --> 00:15:17.167
PIT CHICK?

00:15:17.167 --> 00:15:18.904
GET MOVIN’, THUNDER THIGHS!

00:15:18.904 --> 00:15:19.672
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT’S WITH THE BIG

00:15:19.672 --> 00:15:20.941
CHANGE IN ATTITUDE?

00:15:20.941 --> 00:15:22.377
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS WAY.

00:15:22.377 --> 00:15:23.479
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHERE, EXACTLY, ARE WE

00:15:23.479 --> 00:15:24.014
GOING?

00:15:24.014 --> 00:15:24.682
&gt;&gt; Simon: THE FACE.

00:15:24.682 --> 00:15:25.517
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THE FACE?

00:15:25.517 --> 00:15:26.653
&gt;&gt; Simon: A HUMUNGOUS FACE!

00:15:26.653 --> 00:15:28.022
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DO YOU MEAN A GUNMEN?

00:15:28.022 --> 00:15:28.623
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT THE HELL IS A

00:15:28.623 --> 00:15:29.592
GUNMEN?

00:15:29.592 --> 00:15:30.661
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THAT IS.

00:15:30.661 --> 00:15:33.533
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HUH?

00:15:33.533 --> 00:15:34.468
&gt;&gt; GIVE ME A MINUTE.

00:15:34.468 --> 00:15:35.236
I’M TARGETING ITS POWER

00:15:35.236 --> 00:15:36.906
CONDUITS.

00:15:36.906 --> 00:15:37.675
TAKING THOSE OUT’LL STOP HIM IN

00:15:37.675 --> 00:15:39.277
HIS TRACKS.

00:15:39.277 --> 00:15:40.948
GOTCHA!

00:15:40.948 --> 00:15:42.050
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, YOU WITH THE BIG

00:15:42.050 --> 00:15:42.651
MUG!

00:15:42.651 --> 00:15:43.219
[Yoko gasps]

00:15:43.219 --> 00:15:44.121
WE’RE ABOUT TO TAKE YOU DOWN, SO

00:15:44.121 --> 00:15:45.691
SAY YOUR PRAYERS!

00:15:45.691 --> 00:15:50.333
[laser blasts]

00:15:50.333 --> 00:15:51.201
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT DID YOU DO THAT

00:15:51.201 --> 00:15:52.303
FOR?

00:15:52.303 --> 00:15:53.205
&gt;&gt; Kamina: A MAN LOOKS HIS

00:15:53.205 --> 00:15:54.107
OPPONENT IN THE EYE WHEN HE LETS

00:15:54.107 --> 00:15:55.042
HIM HAVE IT.

00:15:55.042 --> 00:15:56.011
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M A WOMAN, THANK YOU

00:15:56.011 --> 00:15:57.013
VERY MUCH!

00:15:57.013 --> 00:15:58.048
&gt;&gt; Kamina: A WOMAN HAS NO PLACE

00:15:58.048 --> 00:15:59.619
MEDDLING IN A FIGHT BETWEEN MEN.

00:15:59.619 --> 00:16:00.654
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M THE ONE WHO’S DOING

00:16:00.654 --> 00:16:01.956
ALL THE FIGHTING.

00:16:01.956 --> 00:16:03.025
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I LIKE YOUR STYLE,

00:16:03.025 --> 00:16:03.527
LADY.

00:16:03.527 --> 00:16:07.333
YOU’VE GOT A LOT OF SPUNK.

00:16:07.333 --> 00:16:08.235
THIS IS IT?

00:16:08.235 --> 00:16:10.039
THE FACE YOU WANTED TO SHOW ME?

00:16:10.039 --> 00:16:10.541
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH.

00:16:10.541 --> 00:16:11.375
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THIS MAKES TWO

00:16:11.375 --> 00:16:13.680
AWESOME THINGS YOU’VE DUG UP.

00:16:13.680 --> 00:16:14.982
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HEY, I WONDER IF THIS

00:16:14.982 --> 00:16:16.451
IS A FRIEND OF THE OTHER GUNMEN.

00:16:16.451 --> 00:16:17.420
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IT’S SMALLER THAN THE

00:16:17.420 --> 00:16:19.224
THING UP THERE, BUT I KIND OF

00:16:19.224 --> 00:16:20.092
LIKE ITS FACE.

00:16:20.092 --> 00:16:22.096
&gt;&gt; Simon: THEN CHECK THIS OUT!

00:16:22.096 --> 00:16:23.132
&gt;&gt; Yoko: PEOPLE RIDE IN IT?

00:16:23.132 --> 00:16:24.167
THAT’S IMPOSSIBLE.

00:16:24.167 --> 00:16:25.369
&gt;&gt; Kamina: CAN WE DRIVE IT?

00:16:25.369 --> 00:16:26.338
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, BRO, LET’S USE

00:16:26.338 --> 00:16:27.675
THIS TO TAKE OUT THAT THING UP

00:16:27.675 --> 00:16:28.543
THERE.

00:16:28.543 --> 00:16:30.179
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YEAH, LET’S WASTE IT.

00:16:30.179 --> 00:16:31.114
&gt;&gt; UH‐HUH.

00:16:31.114 --> 00:16:32.050
&gt;&gt; WITH THIS, HUH?

00:16:32.050 --> 00:16:33.252
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT’S RIGHT, BRO!

00:16:33.252 --> 00:16:34.254
YOU CAN USE THIS TO‐‐

00:16:34.254 --> 00:16:37.995
WHAT THE‐‐

00:16:37.995 --> 00:16:39.632
I THINK IT’S RUNNING.

00:16:39.632 --> 00:16:40.199
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT?

00:16:40.199 --> 00:16:40.701
ARE YOU SURE?

00:16:40.701 --> 00:16:41.736
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME ON, BRO!

00:16:41.736 --> 00:16:44.074
GO FOR IT!

00:16:44.074 --> 00:16:45.476
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I THINK YOU SHOULD DO

00:16:45.476 --> 00:16:46.078
IT, SIMON.

00:16:46.078 --> 00:16:46.746
[gasps]

00:16:46.746 --> 00:16:48.115
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE THE ONE WHO DUG THIS

00:16:48.115 --> 00:16:48.650
THING UP.

00:16:48.650 --> 00:16:50.286
THAT MEANS IT BELONGS TO YOU.

00:16:50.286 --> 00:16:51.255
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT I‐‐

00:16:51.255 --> 00:16:52.423
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU THINK THE GREAT

00:16:52.423 --> 00:16:53.225
KAMINA COULD STEAL FROM HIS

00:16:53.225 --> 00:16:54.127
BROTHER?

00:16:54.127 --> 00:16:54.996
WHAT KIND OF A PERSON DO YOU

00:16:54.996 --> 00:16:56.398
THINK YOU’RE DEALING WITH?

00:16:56.398 --> 00:16:57.100
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT?

00:16:57.100 --> 00:16:58.737
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT I CAN’T DO THIS.

00:16:58.737 --> 00:17:00.541
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU DUMB‐ASS!

00:17:00.541 --> 00:17:01.643
KICK LOGIC OUT AND DO THE

00:17:01.643 --> 00:17:03.279
IMPOSSIBLE.

00:17:03.279 --> 00:17:04.381
REMEMBER THAT.

00:17:04.381 --> 00:17:05.651
THAT’S THE WAY TEAM GURREN

00:17:05.651 --> 00:17:06.519
ROLLS!

00:17:06.519 --> 00:17:07.655
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT I‐‐

00:17:07.655 --> 00:17:09.692
[rumbling]

00:17:09.692 --> 00:17:14.134
[roaring]

00:17:14.134 --> 00:17:14.602
&gt;&gt; Kamina: JUST DO IT!

00:17:14.602 --> 00:17:17.575
[squeaks]

00:17:17.575 --> 00:17:18.643
&gt;&gt; GO ON.

00:17:18.643 --> 00:17:19.779
I KNOW YOU CAN DO IT, BUDDY!

00:17:19.779 --> 00:17:22.016
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT I DON’T!

00:17:22.016 --> 00:17:23.118
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LISTEN, SIMON.

00:17:23.118 --> 00:17:24.487
DON’T BELIEVE IN YOURSELF.

00:17:24.487 --> 00:17:26.325
BELIEVE IN ME.

00:17:26.325 --> 00:17:28.062
BELIEVE IN THE KAMINA WHO

00:17:28.062 --> 00:17:28.597
BELIEVES IN YOU.

00:17:28.597 --> 00:17:31.603
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT’S THAT MEAN?

00:17:31.603 --> 00:17:36.746
&gt;&gt; Simon: RIGHT, I’LL TRY.

00:17:36.746 --> 00:17:37.748
[upbeat adventurous music]

00:17:37.748 --> 00:17:45.764
♪ ♪

00:17:45.764 --> 00:17:49.070
[squeaks]

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:49.437
[pulsing]

00:17:49.437 --> 00:17:57.521
♪ ♪

00:18:02.497 --> 00:18:06.739
[electronic whirring]

00:18:06.739 --> 00:18:10.847
[mechanical clanging]

00:18:10.847 --> 00:18:13.185
IT’S WORKING!

00:18:13.185 --> 00:18:21.268
[screaming]

00:18:24.542 --> 00:18:25.544
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YEAH!

00:18:25.544 --> 00:18:26.846
YOU DID IT, SIMON!

00:18:26.846 --> 00:18:27.748
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, YEAH, I GUESS I

00:18:27.748 --> 00:18:28.282
DID!

00:18:28.282 --> 00:18:32.256
&gt;&gt; Kamina: COME ON, LET’S ROCK!

00:18:32.256 --> 00:18:33.359
&gt;&gt; Mayor: HEY, WAIT, THAT’S‐‐

00:18:33.359 --> 00:18:35.396
KAMINA AND SIMON?

00:18:35.396 --> 00:18:37.433
[Kamina laughs]

00:18:37.433 --> 00:18:38.603
YOU WEREN’T EXPECTING THIS,

00:18:38.603 --> 00:18:39.471
YOU S. O. B.

00:18:39.471 --> 00:18:40.841
EVEN IF HEAVEN ITSELF TOLERATES

00:18:40.841 --> 00:18:41.876
YOUR BRUTALITY, THE MIGHTY

00:18:41.876 --> 00:18:43.847
LAGANN DOES NOT!

00:18:43.847 --> 00:18:45.149
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT IS LAGANN?

00:18:45.149 --> 00:18:46.284
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IT’S THIS BIG FELLA’S

00:18:46.284 --> 00:18:46.853
NAME.

00:18:46.853 --> 00:18:52.531
I JUST CAME UP WITH IT.

00:18:52.531 --> 00:18:54.635
SIMON, WHY ARE YOU DODGING?

00:18:54.635 --> 00:18:55.269
QUIT RUNNING!

00:18:55.269 --> 00:18:56.138
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT IT’S GONNA KILL

00:18:56.138 --> 00:18:57.407
US!

00:18:57.407 --> 00:18:58.342
&gt;&gt; Kamina: A REAL MAN WOULD

00:18:58.342 --> 00:18:59.779
RATHER DIE THAN RUN!

00:18:59.779 --> 00:19:01.281
[roars]

00:19:01.281 --> 00:19:09.364
[screaming]

00:19:10.132 --> 00:19:10.901
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WE’RE ON TOP OF ITS

00:19:10.901 --> 00:19:16.913
HEAD?

00:19:16.913 --> 00:19:21.254
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, BRO!

00:19:21.254 --> 00:19:22.758
&gt;&gt; Yoko: STAY AWAY!

00:19:22.758 --> 00:19:26.666
[screaming and gasping]

00:19:26.666 --> 00:19:28.703
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOU GOT TO MAKE THE

00:19:28.703 --> 00:19:31.241
IMPOSSIBLE POSSIBLE!

00:19:31.241 --> 00:19:34.280
THAT’S HOW TEAM GURREN ROLLS!

00:19:34.280 --> 00:19:39.558
[screaming]

00:19:39.558 --> 00:19:44.802
I’M COMING, BRO!

00:19:44.802 --> 00:19:46.338
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SIMON, PRETTY SLICK,

00:19:46.338 --> 00:19:46.839
MAN.

00:19:46.839 --> 00:19:47.841
&gt;&gt; Yoko: COME ON, LET’S JUMP.

00:19:47.841 --> 00:19:49.210
MAKE IT JUMP.

00:19:49.210 --> 00:19:50.547
HEY, QUIT WASTING TIME AND HURRY

00:19:50.547 --> 00:19:54.187
UP!

00:19:54.187 --> 00:19:58.228
[metallic clang]

00:19:58.228 --> 00:20:00.433
[deep groan]

00:20:05.844 --> 00:20:10.186
[crash]

00:20:10.186 --> 00:20:11.789
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, NICE WORK WITH

00:20:11.789 --> 00:20:12.758
THE CANOPY, SIMON.

00:20:12.758 --> 00:20:13.593
&gt;&gt; Yoko: IT’S A LITTLE BIT

00:20:13.593 --> 00:20:16.431
CRAMPED, THOUGH.

00:20:16.431 --> 00:20:17.701
&gt;&gt; Kamina: ALL RIGHT.

00:20:17.701 --> 00:20:18.603
WE TOOK IT DOWN.

00:20:18.603 --> 00:20:19.705
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I GUESS THIS THING’S

00:20:19.705 --> 00:20:20.874
HEAD IS HARD AS A ROCK.

00:20:20.874 --> 00:20:25.249
[screams]

00:20:25.249 --> 00:20:28.322
[deep laughter]

00:20:28.322 --> 00:20:32.296
I HAVE YOU NOW!

00:20:32.296 --> 00:20:33.867
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WE’RE DONE FOR!

00:20:33.867 --> 00:20:34.835
IT’S SO CRAMPED.

00:20:34.835 --> 00:20:36.238
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, QUIT MAKING ALL

00:20:36.238 --> 00:20:36.839
THOSE WEIRD LITTLE SOUNDS OVER

00:20:36.839 --> 00:20:37.641
THERE.

00:20:37.641 --> 00:20:38.543
&gt;&gt; Simon: DAMN IT.

00:20:38.543 --> 00:20:39.512
POWER!

00:20:39.512 --> 00:20:41.716
NEED MORE POWER!

00:20:41.716 --> 00:20:44.220
[straining]

00:20:51.969 --> 00:20:54.274
[electronic whirring]

00:20:54.274 --> 00:20:55.977
[explosion]

00:20:55.977 --> 00:20:57.413
&gt;&gt; Kamina: A DRILL?

00:20:57.413 --> 00:20:58.449
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT SORT OF POPPED OUT.

00:20:58.449 --> 00:20:59.284
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THAT’S YOUR KIND OF

00:20:59.284 --> 00:20:59.785
WEAPON.

00:20:59.785 --> 00:21:02.390
IT’S A PERFECT MATCH!

00:21:02.390 --> 00:21:03.993
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO, I THINK I’LL BE

00:21:03.993 --> 00:21:04.929
ABLE TO DO THE JOB WITH THIS!

00:21:04.929 --> 00:21:06.398
&gt;&gt; Kamina: ALL RIGHT, SMASH US

00:21:06.398 --> 00:21:08.603
INTO THAT BIG UGLY MUG.

00:21:08.603 --> 00:21:09.705
LET IT FEEL THE POWER OF TEAM

00:21:09.705 --> 00:21:14.414
GURREN’S MIGHTY DRILL!

00:21:14.414 --> 00:21:17.821
[screams]

00:21:17.821 --> 00:21:18.923
&gt;&gt; Kamina: GET GOING, SIMON.

00:21:18.923 --> 00:21:20.827
BUST THROUGH THE HEAVENS WITH

00:21:20.827 --> 00:21:24.334
YOUR DRILL!

00:21:24.334 --> 00:21:26.906
[screaming]

00:21:33.853 --> 00:21:37.628
[growls]

00:21:46.044 --> 00:21:49.484
[gasps]

00:21:57.801 --> 00:22:03.646
[sighs]

00:22:03.646 --> 00:22:07.721
[electronic whirring]

00:22:07.721 --> 00:22:09.859
&gt;&gt; ADIOS, GIHA VILLAGE.

00:22:09.859 --> 00:22:11.562
WE’RE GOING UP TO THE SURFACE!

00:22:11.562 --> 00:22:13.967
THE SURFACE I SAW AS A KID.

00:22:13.967 --> 00:22:19.812
[straining]

00:22:19.812 --> 00:22:22.016
[screaming]

00:22:27.828 --> 00:22:28.830
[triumphant music]

00:22:28.830 --> 00:22:36.913
♪ ♪

00:22:42.858 --> 00:22:43.626
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WOW, THIS IS THE

00:22:43.626 --> 00:22:45.564
SURFACE?

00:22:55.951 --> 00:22:58.488
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT’S SO BEAUTIFUL.

00:22:58.488 --> 00:23:00.426
&gt;&gt; Yoko: IT’S YOKO.

00:23:00.426 --> 00:23:02.496
YOKO IS MY NAME.

00:23:02.496 --> 00:23:03.833
I NEVER INTRODUCED MYSELF,

00:23:03.833 --> 00:23:04.367
DID I?

00:23:04.367 --> 00:23:05.971
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME TO THINK OF IT‐‐

00:23:05.971 --> 00:23:07.406
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I’M KAMINA.

00:23:07.406 --> 00:23:08.442
THIS IS SIMON.

00:23:08.442 --> 00:23:11.782
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NICE TO MEET YOU.

00:23:11.782 --> 00:23:13.151
UM, WHAT IS THIS LITTLE FURRY

00:23:13.151 --> 00:23:14.420
THING THAT’S BEEN HIDING OUT

00:23:14.420 --> 00:23:15.389
IN MY CLEAVAGE?

00:23:15.389 --> 00:23:16.124
&gt;&gt; Simon: BOOTA,

00:23:16.124 --> 00:23:17.159
BEHAVE YOURSELF.

00:23:17.159 --> 00:23:18.963
&gt;&gt; Kamina: A TASTY MORSEL HIDING

00:23:18.963 --> 00:23:20.099
IN MORE TASTY MORSELS.

00:23:20.099 --> 00:23:20.967
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HEY, IS IT JUST ME, OR

00:23:20.967 --> 00:23:22.169
ARE WE FALLING?

00:23:22.169 --> 00:23:23.005
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, THE THRUSTERS

00:23:23.005 --> 00:23:23.740
TURNED OFF!

00:23:23.740 --> 00:23:24.575
DO SOMETHING!

00:23:24.575 --> 00:23:26.378
&gt;&gt; Simon: I DON’T KNOW HOW!

00:23:26.378 --> 00:23:27.681
IT’S NO USE!

00:23:27.681 --> 00:23:28.850
&gt;&gt; Yoko: GREAT.

00:23:28.850 --> 00:23:31.522
[screaming]

00:23:31.522 --> 00:23:32.691
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WE’RE FALLING!

00:23:32.691 --> 00:23:36.899
TRY TO HOLD ON TIGHT!

00:23:36.899 --> 00:23:39.505
[crash]

00:23:47.554 --> 00:23:49.525
TALK ABOUT A ROUGH RECEPTION.

00:23:49.525 --> 00:23:53.031
&gt;&gt; Simon: NO KIDDING.

00:23:53.031 --> 00:23:58.543
I‐I’M SORRY.

00:23:58.543 --> 00:24:03.485
[gasps]

00:24:03.485 --> 00:24:04.688
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH, GREAT, OUT OF

00:24:04.688 --> 00:24:06.826
THE FRYING PAN, INTO THE FIRE.

00:24:06.826 --> 00:24:08.596
[growling]

00:24:17.013 --> 00:24:18.015
[rock music]

00:24:18.015 --> 00:24:24.494
♪ ♪

00:24:24.494 --> 00:24:25.496
[man singing in Japanese]

00:24:25.496 --> 00:24:33.546
♪ ♪

00:25:47.761 --> 00:25:48.730
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IF YOU’RE DOING IT,

00:25:48.730 --> 00:25:49.998
THEN SO AM I.

00:25:49.998 --> 00:25:51.969
IF I DON’T DO IT, WILL YOU?

00:25:51.969 --> 00:25:53.873
IF YOU DON’T DO IT, I WILL!

00:25:53.873 --> 00:25:54.742
I’M DOING IT, SO YOU DO IT TOO,

00:25:54.742 --> 00:25:55.944
DAMN IT!

00:25:55.944 --> 00:25:58.716
NEXT TIME, ON <i>GURREN LAGANN...</i>

00:25:58.716 --> 00:26:00.219
"I SAID I’M GONNA PILOT

00:26:00.219 --> 00:26:02.691
THAT THING!!"

